snippet.title: TV Schedule | Cartoon Network Show Listings
snippet.description: Find a complete schedule of local listings for all your favorite shows. Discover what to watch and when to find it on Cartoon Network.

snippet.title: Darkness Shall Rise
snippet.description: Just as the rebuilding effort in Ninjago begins, the four ninjas come to realize that evil has started to resurface with Lord Garmadon forging the ninjas' lost Golden Weapons into a Mega-Weapon with unspeakable powers.

snippet.title: LEGO Star Wars - The Dark Side Rises
snippet.description: Count Dooku carries a broken General Grievous across an active battlefield to get the cloning material back to his master. Watch more LEGO Star Wars Yoda Chronicles videos at LEGO.com!

snippet.title: Rise of the Spinjitzu Master
snippet.description: A great darkness has fallen upon Ninjago as Garmadon's Super-Weapon has turned it evil but Lloyd and the Ninjas discover that light is more powerful than dark - and the final and ultimate battle is on.

snippet.title: Knights Retreat
snippet.description: The Knights have to retreat when they run low on Tenkai Energy. Watch more Tenkai Knights on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Storm Cannon
snippet.description: The Knights try a desperate attack against Vilius' Storm Cannon. Watch more Tenkai Knights on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Dark Knight at the Museum
snippet.description: Batman freaks out when the displays at the Museum of Television come to life. Watch more MAD on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: Ribeye Knights
snippet.description: The Ribeye Knights recruit Johnny to help them defeat the evil Dark Vegan. Watch more Johnny Test on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: The Chosen One
snippet.description: When Johnny fails the training, the Ribeye Knights give him temporary powers. Watch more Johnny Test on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: The Dark Knight Falls
snippet.description: Batman's battle with Gentleman Ghost in London might be his last! Watch more Batman: The Brave and the Bold on Cartoon Network!
